The 1 mM BTH solution was prepared by dissolving 42 mg of the pure BTH (trade name Acibenzolar-S-methyl, Merck KGaA, Darmstadt, Germany) in 10 ml of HPLC grade acetone (Carl Roth GmbH, Karlsruhe, Germany). Afterwards the solution was poured in 20 ml of double distilled water, together with 100 \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
