In test measurements with empty cuvettes and cuvettes containing pots with barley we investigated the temperature and humidity dynamics inside the cuvette relative to the temperature and humidity in the phytotron chamber housing of the cuvette system (see “Methodology” section). During this experiment, also the cuvette inlet air flows and the light conditions were changed. Figure 4 illustrates the results of this physical characterisation. Apparently, when altering the temperature of the chamber, the cuvette temperature changed at a time scale \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
